yir 0.1

resource cpu0 cpu.arm64

cpu.const base cpu0 5
cpu.const shift cpu0 3
cpu.shl wide cpu0 base shift
cpu.const mask cpu0 7
cpu.or mixed cpu0 wide mask
cpu.xor result cpu0 mixed base
cpu.print out cpu0 result

edge dep base wide
edge dep shift wide
edge dep wide mixed
edge dep mask mixed
edge dep mixed result
edge dep base result
edge dep result out
edge effect result out
